---
title: Cal Smart Honey Double Pork Chops with Snap Peas and Garlicky Rice
description: Sweet and savoury meet in our honey-glazed pork chops with pan-fried snap peas. Bold garlic, zesty green onions and sweet honey lighten up this homemade riff on a takeout fave.

